arts.ttl: When is Ecuador - Bolivia? how to watch on TV, stream online
arts.sum: Bolivia, playing at home at a higher altitude than Ecuador, is accustomed to the challenging climate, which makes the game intriguing. The game between Ecuador - Bolivia will be played on Thursday November 14, with kick off at 7:00 p.m. ET / 4:00 p.m. PT.

arts.ttl: When is Colombia vs Ecuador? Times, how to watch on TV and stream online
arts.sum: On matchday 12 of South America’s World Cup qualifying competition, Colombia continue their bid for a return to the global tournament as they host an Ecuador team chasing back-to-back berths at the event. Having won five of their first 10 games - including victories over Brazil and world champions Argentina - Los Cafeteros headed into November’s international week sitting second in CONMEBOL’s 10-team qualifying group, from which the top six will qualify automatically for next year’s finals.

arts.ttl: When is Bolivia vs Paraguay? Times, how to watch on TV and stream online
arts.sum: Bolivia host Paraguay on matchday 12 of South America’s men’s World Cup qualifying competition, in a clash between two nations that are out to end long waits to return to FIFA’s flagship international tournament. Having failed to qualify for the World Cup since 1994, Bolivia went into November international week sitting seventh in CONMEBOL’s 10-team qualifying group - one point behind sixth-placed Paraguay, who last made the finals in 2010.
